ver known, and his life beyond the music. His journey from the discovery of his extraordinary talent as the lead of the Jackson Five, to the visionary artist whose creative ambition fueled a relentless pursuit to become the biggest entertainer in the world, highlighting both his life off-stage and some of the most iconic performances from his early solo career.\",\"popularity\":512.4438,\"poster_path\":\"/zm0KAbOjlt9eR5y7vDiL2dEOwMl.jpg\",\"release_date\":\"2026-04-22\",\"softcore\":false,\"video\":false,\"vote_average\":8.647,\"vote_count\":2547},{\"adult\":false,\"backdrop_path\":\"/oPsRr7AfNLw6XaPuMpvkWK0bIUA.jpg\",\"genre_ids\":[28,18],\"id\":1057265,\"title\":\"Peddi\",\"original_language\":\"te\",\"original_title\":\"పెద్ది\",\"overview\":\"In 1980s rural Andhra Pradesh, a spirited villager unites his community through sports to defend their pride against a powerful rival.\",\"popularity\":361.9352,\"poster_path\":\"/kJAJNNBYlbqAcpTDxBNnaILSMTy.jpg\",\"release_date\":\"2026-06-03\",\"softcore\":false,\"video\":false,\"vote_average\":6.547,\"vote_count\":43},{\"adult\":false,\"backdrop_path\":\"/1eAuwNBy34kkM3xkl202z4f1NiI.jpg\",\"genre_ids\":[28,14],\"id\":1367220,\"title\":\"Karuppu\",\"original_language\":\"ta\",\"original_title\":\"கருப்பு\",\"overview\":\"In a world where justice falters, guardian deity Vettai Karuppu takes the guise of a lawyer to battle a corrupt legal system preying on the powerless.\",\"popularity\":413.7865,\"poster_path\":\"/4KZXlZ5tTT6ghbW77gS4hSLkCd7.jpg\",\"release_date\":\"2026-05-14\",\"softcore\":false,\"video\":false,\"vote_average\":7.059,\"vote_count\":17},{\"adult\":false,\"backdrop_path\":\"/7uXzE0ZBkbAeKylOz7cUQF4Yw75.jpg\",\"genre_ids\":[18],\"id\":879945,\"title\":\"The Unknown Man\",\"original_language\":\"nl\",\"original_title\":\"L'homme inconnu\",\"overview\":\"Louis, a Flemish writer, decides to isolate himself at the Côte d’Azur, hoping this place will bring him inspiration.\",\"popularity\":378.8827,\"poster_path\":\"/4TpBhdaSl5ALHbgeaYOLF8Q3haz.jpg\",\"release_date\":\"2021-10-16\",\"softcore\":false,\"video\":false,\"vote_average\":7.8,\"vote_count\":9},{\"adult\":false,\"backdrop_path\":\"/l5QgEvlfK6eHPM4YPEk7AArXmh8.jpg\",\"genre_ids\":[10749,35],\"id\":1308553,\"title\":\"Hai Jawani Toh Ishq Hona Hai\",\"original_language\":\"hi\",\"original_title\":\"है जवानी तो इश्क होना है\",\"overview\":\"When Jass leaves his marriage over conflicting priorities, a new romance abroad is upended by shocking revelations, forcing him to confront love, loyalty, and the true meaning of commitment.\",\"popularity\":289.6886,\"poster_path\":\"/vmlJvz6qVzYgei2V74GvnmcuQfW.jpg\",\"release_date\":\"2026-06-04\",\"softcore\":false,\"video\":false,\"vote_average\":5.471,\"vote_count\":17},{\"adult\":false,\"backdrop_path\":\"/s6ly8laenkHWlIBRkLSfIuEMLC6.jpg\",\"genre_ids\":[53,878,28],\"id\":1275779,\"title\":\"Disclosure Day\",\"original_language\":\"en\",\"original_title\":\"Disclosure Day\",\"overview\":\"If you found out we weren’t alone, if someone showed you, proved it to you, would that frighten you?\",\"popularity\":326.4035,\"poster_path\":\"/3o5YPjDGDTcTDL5ftDA9NwN9dLd.jpg\",\"release_date\":\"2026-06-10\",\"softcore\":false,\"video\":false,\"vote_average\":6.8,\"vote_count\":468},{\"adult\":false,\"backdrop_path\":\"/A2tzVTVtnTvpji96IZmleN78KKv.jpg\",\"genre_ids\":[27,35],\"id\":1239134,\"title\":\"Bhooth Bangla\",\"original_language\":\"hi\",\"original_title\":\"भूत बंगला\",\"overview\":\"A man inherits a palace in rural Mangalpur and plans his sister's wedding there, but strange supernatural events and panicked locals force him to investigate the property's mysterious past.\",\"popularity\":337.3635,\"poster_path\":\"/79RBp8afL4u4z3nVGR78z6eIvBB.jpg\",\"release_date\":\"2026-04-16\",\"softcore\":false,\"video\":false,\"vote_average\":5.5,\"vote_count\":20},{\"adult\":false,\"backdrop_path\":\"/9Z2uDYXqJrlmePznQQJhL6d92Rq.jpg\",\"genre_ids\":[10751,35,12,14,16],\"id\":1226863,\"title\":\"The Super Mario Galaxy Movie\",\"original_language\":\"en\",\"original_title\":\"The Super Mario Galaxy Movie\",\"overview\":\"Having thwarted Bowser's previous plot to marry Princess Peach, Mario and Luigi now face a fresh threat in Bowser Jr., who is determined to liberate his father from captivity and restore the family legacy. Alongside companions new and old, the brothers travel across the stars to stop the young heir's crusade.\",\"popularity\":243.6128,\"poster_path\":\"/eJGWx219ZcEMVQJhAgMiqo8tYY.jpg\",\"release_date\":\"2026-04-01\",\"softcore\":false,\"video\":false,\"vote_average\":8.19,\"vote_count\":2647},{\"adult\":false,\"backdrop_path\":\"/6zg7A9ICOthNR2TSXlT51KvXrsA.jpg\",\"genre_ids\":[28,12,878],\"id\":1228710,\"title\":\"The Mandalorian and Grogu\",\"original_language\":\"en\",\"original_title\":\"The Mandalorian and Grogu\",\"overview\":\"The evil Empire has fallen, and Imperial warlords remain scattered throughout the galaxy. As the fledgling New Republic works to protect everything the Rebellion fought for, they have enlisted the help of legendary Mandalorian bounty hunter Din Djarin and his young apprentice Grogu.\",\"popularity\":239.2479,\"poster_path\":\"/5Vi8dSauVwH1HOsiZceDMbRr1Ca.jpg\",\"release_date\":\"2026-05-20\",\"softcore\":false,\"video\":false,\"vote_average\":6.769,\"vote_count\":478},{\"adult\":false,\"backdrop_path\":\"/emK2hOB6ACiExT0lNLog9lAmMFL.jpg\",\"genre_ids\":[18,10749],\"id\":1226293,\"title\":\"Salitan\",\"original_language\":\"tl\",\"original_title\":\"Salitan\",\"overview\":\"A suspicious wife follows her husband in Bali. She meets a dashing man who captures her heart. She soon wants her husband to really have an affair to alleviate the guilt she is feeling.\",\"popularity\":231.5883,\"poster_path\":\"/rMgG7cWuq9O6zhhLs2CbqIKVA8V.jpg\",\"release_date\":\"2024-02-16\",\"softcore\":false,\"video\":false,\"vote_average\":4.714,\"vote_count\":7},{\"adult\":false,\"backdrop_path\":null,\"genre_ids\":[18],\"id\":